mouseclock for DEBIAN
----------------------

Mouseclock -- a little program to display the current time using the X
root cursor.
To get a big, friendly mouse pointer :
mouseclock -fn "-b&h-lucida-bold-i-normal-sans-18-180-75-75-p-119-iso8859-1" -fg \#ffa0a0 -bd 2 &
We applied patch-01 of David O'Brien, which adds option -12hr.

